---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Caterham Specialist" description="Over 30 years of Caterham 7 experience. Bespoke builds, GSXR conversions, suspension setup, and complete engineering services.">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero caterham-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
      <h1>Caterham <span class="text-green">Specialist</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Over 30 years owning, racing, and developing Caterham 7s. From suspension setup to complete bespoke builds.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>The Car That's "Too Fast To Race"</h2>
          <p>The Caterham Seven was banned from racing in the US in the 1960s, and again in the UK in the 1970s – for being "Too fast to race". That heritage is in our name and in our DNA.</p>
          <p>Simon has been involved with Caterhams since the beginning of his motorsport career. Competing, developing, building, and refining these incredible machines. There's no better platform for understanding vehicle dynamics and suspension engineering.</p>
          <p>Whether you need your existing car optimised, want a bespoke build created to your exact specification, or are considering a bike engine conversion – we have the experience and expertise to deliver.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-stats">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">30+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years with Caterhams</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">390kg</span>
            <span class="stat-label">GSXR Build Weight</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">290bhp</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Kawasaki H2 Power</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="caterham-services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
        <h2>Caterham Services</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card large">
          <div class="service-card-content">
            <h3>Bespoke Builds</h3>
            <p>Your Caterham, built your way. We work with you from concept to completion – specifying components, building to the highest standards, and developing the setup to suit your requirements. First pneumatic paddle shift 7 in 2005. Full tractions controll and closed loop paddleshift in 2012. First Caterham Ecoboost in 2018. Fully independent rear double wishbone suspension 7 2020.  Caterham GSXR (L7) 390kg and 250bhp 2021. Caterham Kawasaki H2 Supercharged - stock engine - 2024. </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Full build service from kit or donor</li>
              <li>Component selection and specification</li>
              <li>Engine and transmission options</li>
              <li>Suspension setup and development</li>
              <li>Rolling road tuning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card-content">
            <h3>GSXR Conversions</h3>
            <p>The Suzuki GSXR engine transforms the Caterham experience. 250bhp in a 390kg car delivers extraordinary performance with the soundtrack to match.</p>
            <p>We have extensive experience with bike-engined Sevens and can guide you through the conversion process or build a complete car to your specification.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card-content">
            <h3>Suspension Setup</h3>
            <p>Every Caterham we've owned or developed has taught us something. That accumulated knowledge goes into every setup we deliver.</p>
            <p>From standard Sigma cars to full race-spec, we dial in suspension that makes your car communicate clearly and respond predictably.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card-content">
            <h3>Servicing & Maintenance</h3>
            <p>Regular servicing by someone who understands Caterhams keeps your car reliable and performing at its best. We catch issues before they become problems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card-content">
            <h3>Upgrades & Modifications</h3>
            <p>Suspension upgrades, engine work, braking improvements, weight reduction – we can advise on and implement modifications that genuinely improve your car.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Build -->
  <section class="featured-build">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="build-grid">
        <div class="build-content">
          <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
          <h2>The GSXR Build</h2>
          <p class="lead">390kg · 250bhp · Pure Driving</p>
          <p>Our GSXR-powered Caterham represents the pinnacle of what the Seven platform can deliver. Lightweight, powerful, and developed through countless hours of testing and refinement.</p>
          
          <div class="build-specs">
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Engine</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Suzuki GSXR 1000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Power</span>
              <span class="spec-value">250bhp @ 10,000rpm</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Weight</span>
              <span class="spec-value">390kg</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Power/Weight</span>
              <span class="spec-value">641bhp/tonne</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p>This level of performance demands suspension that can keep up. Every aspect of the chassis has been developed to work with the engine's character – predictable, communicative, and ultimately fast.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="build-image">
          <img src="/images/Simon__R_Project_FF_204.png" alt="Caterham GSXR Build" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Us -->
  <section class="why-us">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
        <h2>Why Choose Us for Your Caterham</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="reasons-grid">
        <div class="reason">
          <h4>Experience</h4>
          <p>30+ years of hands-on Caterham ownership, racing, and development. We've made the mistakes so you don't have to.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reason">
          <h4>Results</h4>
          <p>Championship wins and podium finishes at hillclimbs across the UK. We know what it takes to be competitive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reason">
          <h4>Engineering Depth</h4>
          <p>Founded RaceShocks.UK and CORE Suspension. Worked with TracTive, Penske, Nitron. We understand dampers at a fundamental level.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reason">
          <h4>Personal Service</h4>
          <p>When you work with us, you work with Simon. Direct communication, no layers – just expert advice and quality work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Let's Build Something Special</h2>
        <p>Whether it's a setup consultation or a complete bespoke build – get in touch to discuss your project.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.2);
  }

  .caterham-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .caterham-hero .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: 
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9) 0%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.7) 100%),
      url('/images/Simon__R_Project_FF_203.png') center/cover no-repeat;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Intro */
  .intro-section {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .intro-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .intro-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .intro-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--tftr-green);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-card .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-card .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--tftr-grey);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* Services Grid */
  .caterham-services {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .section-header.centered {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--tftr-dark);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .service-card.large {
    grid-column: span 1;
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .service-card-content {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--tftr-green);
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-card ul {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .service-card li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .service-card li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
  }

  /* Featured Build */
  .featured-build {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .build-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .build-content .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .build-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .build-specs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .spec {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--tftr-grey);
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .build-image {
    position: relative;
  }

  .build-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* Why Us */
  .why-us {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .reasons-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .reason {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
  }

  .reason h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .reason p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tftr-green-dark), var(--tftr-green));
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: var(--space-sm) auto var(--space-md);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    
    .service-card.large {
      grid-column: span 2;
      grid-row: span 1;
    }
    
    .reasons-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .intro-stats {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-card {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 150px;
    }
    
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .service-card.large {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .build-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .build-image {
      order: -1;
    }
    
    .reasons-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
